 invalidated the sessions of all\nrole members synchronously on the request thread, loading every member\nuser twice (once via UserRole.getUsers, once via getUserByUsername) and\nbuilding full UserDetails per member. On a role with ~640 members this\nmade the PATCH take ~7s and allocate ~1.4GB.\n\ninvalidateUserSessions now expires sessions using a thin username-only\nprincipal: UserDetailsImpl equality includes username only and the\nRedis-backed session registry resolves principals by name, so no user\nneeds to be loaded. UserRoleBundleHook publishes an event instead of\niterating members, and a listener invalidates the sessions after commit\non a dedicated single-threaded executor, in batches with a pause in\nbetween, using a usernames-by-role query.","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"96a4b0f610b310a1b54d40e304eea2dee6d8e878","tree_id":"146cbf9a8bef11b82223f512fd61a43d6fe64987","timestamp":"2026-07-18T19:09:06Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starr